This file marks the directory as opt-in: bake's recursive discovery skips it,
so broad targets like `bake build test` and `bake build test/integration` will
not try to fetch and build flecs-engine's bundles. Build it explicitly with:

    bake build test/integration/flecs-engine

Building this project requires cmake and cargo on PATH, plus a macOS host (the
upstream sources only ship a Cocoa native surface).
